name: Linda Lina
description:
I am simple girl, honest, loyal and sweet woman who’s looking for a good man. I am a religious woman and passionate. I love listening to music, to cook and play computer. also hardworking, cheerful, affectionate and a happy woman who is easy-going, humble, nice, faithful, loyal woman.
I’m searching for my right man, the one who is good, loyal, faithful, responsible honest, respectful, loving, God-fearing, caring and family oriented. A man who can grow old with me and build a happy family.
